node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Salice Rose on August 22, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Tweet Salice Rose @salice_roseee What's something you regret doing? 7:53 AM 8/22/21 Twitter for iPhone'.

node.text: Vent below.❤️ I used to say “I don’t regret anything cause everything I went through made me the person I am today” but I changed my answer. Although that’s true…we also sometimes let ourselves stay in bad or toxic situations when we know better. I have a few regrets because realistically I know right from wrong…. but my BIGGEST regret is thinking people have the same heart as me. I wouldn’t see people for who they were but more so for who they pretended to be…I would see them for who i wanted them to be when deep down i knew they were horrible people. But I learned from ALL that shit & I’m stronger now. What about you? ❤️
